pageProduct.name: PAW Osteocare Chews 300g
pageProduct.description:
General Information

With Glucosamine Sulfate & Chondroitin Sulfate, these tasty kangaroo chews provide everyday joint care, helping to improve joint function and health in younger dogs and older dogs over long term use.

Common Uses

500 mg Glucosamine Sulfate: to provide cartilage nutrition for joint cartilage health and joint function. 250 mg Chondroitin Sulfate: is a major component of joint cartilage and is required for cartilage and joint health. Balanced combination of other nutrients for joint health: PAW Osteocare chews also contains other ingredients such as MSM and a balanced blend of vitamins and minerals that work together to maintain the health of your dog’s joints. Highly palatable chew: A tasty kangaroo based chew that is easy to give to your pet on a daily basis.

Ingredients

Rye flour, Kangaroo meat, glucosamine sulfate, soy flour, chondroitin sulfate, sucrose, emulsifiers, binders, salt, Vitamin C, dimethylsulfone (MSM), natural preservatives, manganese gluconate, natural flavour colour.
